      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A civil complaint was filed in\nJustice Hinkle's court yesterday at\nternoon by John Spear against the\nStar Employment agency. This is\na new tack for the prosecution of\nthe agencies against which numer.\nGus complaints have been made\nthat they beat patrons. Spear sues\nfor $3.50 alleged to be due for time\nspent on seeking a job which he\nbought of the agency."
    }
